Lemma 25: inv(add(inv(add(a, inv(b))), inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), inv(add(a, inv(b))))))) = add(a, inv(b)).
Proof:
  inv(add(inv(add(a, inv(b))), inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), inv(add(a, inv(b)))))))
= { by lemma 21 R->L }
  inv(add(inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), add(a, inv(b)))), inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), inv(add(a, inv(b)))))))
= { by axiom 4 (robbins_axiom) }
  add(a, inv(b))

Lemma 26: inv(add(inv(add(X, Y)), inv(add(X, add(inv(add(Y, Z)), inv(add(Y, inv(Z)))))))) = X.
Proof:
