Lemma 28: add(X, inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), inv(add(a, inv(b)))))) = X.
Proof:
  add(X, inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), inv(add(a, inv(b))))))
= { by lemma 13 R->L }
  inv(add(inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), add(X, inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), inv(add(a, inv(b)))))))), inv(add(add(X, inv(add(add(a, inv(b)), inv(add(a, inv(b)))))), inv(add(a, inv(b)))))))
